{"type":"message","id":"bafa15f5","parentId":"894f42ab","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:55:14.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f0l7xsnbkuua_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 19:55 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 2.7k in / 565 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0019\n🗄️ Cache: 98% hit · 111k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 56% left ⏱4m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 19:55 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 2.7k in / 565 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0019\n🗄️ Cache: 98% hit · 111k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 56% left ⏱4m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773921314425}}
