{"type":"message","id":"ab58dc84","parentId":"2d614d05","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:55:20.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Context usage is at 21% — well below the 60% threshold. Everything looks normal. Let me check if there's anything in the working buffer or session state that needs attention.\n\nThe context monitor script itself will run and check things, but from the session status I can see:\n- Context: 41k/200k (21%) — well within safe limits\n- Everything seems normal\n\nI should just reply HEARTBEAT_OK since nothing requires attention. The context is at 21%, well below threshold, and no urgent items are pending.","thinkingSignature":"eeee8d2dedce96f42c94ebfd0827065170d6e16ca0bdcf4ca324ccf7b792904b"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nHEARTBEAT_OK\n\n**Context Monitor Check:**\n- Context usage: **21%** (41k/200k) — well below 60% threshold ✅\n- No compaction needed ✅\n- No blockers or urgent follow-ups pending ✅\n\nSession is healthy, no action needed.\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1820,"output":181,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39012,"cost":{"input":0.000728,"output":0.0002715,"cacheRead":0.00148044,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00247994}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773921314431}}
